        public void setColumnAliasSeparator(java.lang.String separator)
        Specifies separator for column aliases that divides table reference and column name. Separator should contains of characters that are not used in table names, such as: '$' or '__'.

      • setEntityAwareMode

        public void setEntityAwareMode(boolean entityAwareMode)
        Defines entity-aware mode, when resulting collections does not have duplicates. It make sense to enable it only if cache is set. Therefore, enabling smart mode will also enable caching.
